Comment: 0,0:01:25.76,0:01:27.76,Zestiria 2 Romaji Ending,,0,0,0,,CZ Ending
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.20,0:21:33.50,Zestiria 2 Romaji Ending,,0,0,0,, mou dou shiyou mo nai tte mo aru
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.50,0:21:37.00,Zestiria 2 Romaji Ending,,0,0,0,, naru you ni shika nara nakattari
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.00,0:21:40.58,Zestiria 2 Romaji Ending,,0,0,0,, mata oshiyosetekuru sekai
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.58,0:21:46.49,Zestiria 2 Romaji Ending,,0,0,0,,tada dou yatte uketometara ii?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.96,0:21:49.56,Zestiria 2 Romaji Ending,,0,0,0,,It's mean to be
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.62,0:21:57.66,Zestiria 2 Romaji Ending 2,,0,0,0,,boku dake no mono janakunatta yume
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.16,0:22:04.32,Zestiria 2 Romaji Ending 2,,0,0,0,,asu o michibiite
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.32,0:22:08.38,Zestiria 2 Romaji Ending 2,,0,0,0,,genjitsu to Fight unmei ni Dive
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.38,0:22:13.80,Zestiria 2 Romaji Ending 2,,0,0,0,,hotobashiru omoi nan do iki taesou
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.80,0:22:18.00,Zestiria 2 Romaji Ending 2,,0,0,0,,demo tada massugu ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.00,0:22:19.88,Zestiria 2 Romaji Ending 2,,0,0,0,,Don't give up the fight
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.88,0:22:21.80,Zestiria 2 Romaji Ending 2,,0,0,0,,Time to ignite
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.34,0:22:29.20,Zestiria 2 Romaji Ending 2,,0,0,0,,kono mi o kakete idomu sekai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.20,0:22:36.14,Zestiria 2 Romaji Ending 2,,0,0,0,,isso aru ga mama ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.14,0:22:38.16,Zestiria 2 Romaji Ending 2,,0,0,0,,sono subete o
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.16,0:22:40.76,Zestiria 2 Romaji Ending 2,,0,0,0,,tsutsumikomu yo
Comment: 0,0:01:25.76,0:01:27.76,Zestiria 2 Romaji Ending,,0,0,0,,CZ Ending
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.20,0:21:33.50,Zestiria 2 CZ Ending,,0,0,0,,Jsou věci, se kterými nic neuděláme,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.50,0:21:37.00,Zestiria 2 CZ Ending,,0,0,0,,jejichž osud byl už zpečetěn.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.00,0:21:40.58,Zestiria 2 CZ Ending,,0,0,0,,Takže, když nás tento svět napadá,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.58,0:21:46.49,Zestiria 2 CZ Ending,,0,0,0,,co máme dělat?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.96,0:21:49.56,Zestiria 2 CZ Ending,,0,0,0,,Když to tak má být.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.62,0:21:57.66,Zestiria 2 CZ Ending 2,,0,0,0,,Sen, který už dlouho není jen můj,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.16,0:22:04.32,Zestiria 2 CZ Ending 2,,0,0,0,,určí, co přinese zítřek!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.32,0:22:08.38,Zestiria 2 CZ Ending 2,,0,0,0,,Boj s realitou, potápění se do osudu!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.38,0:22:13.80,Zestiria 2 CZ Ending 2,,0,0,0,,Tyto pocity dobře znám.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.80,0:22:18.00,Zestiria 2 CZ Ending 2,,0,0,0,,I když už nestačíš s dechem, tak pokračuj!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.00,0:22:19.88,Zestiria 2 CZ Ending 2,,0,0,0,,Nevzdávej ten boj!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.88,0:22:21.80,Zestiria 2 CZ Ending 2,,0,0,0,,Čas k zažehnutí!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.34,0:22:29.20,Zestiria 2 CZ Ending 2,,0,0,0,,Nasazujeme životy, čelením tomuhle světu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.20,0:22:36.14,Zestiria 2 CZ Ending 2,,0,0,0,,Bez ohledu na to,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.14,0:22:38.16,Zestiria 2 CZ Ending 2,,0,0,0,,jak to všechno dopadne,
